'''謝美伊·碧福特'''（{{lang-en|'''Jermaine Beckford'''}}，{{bd|1983年|12月9日|catIdx=Beckford, Jermaine}}），是一名[[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[足球|足球]][[運動員|運動員]] ，司職[[前鋒_(足球)|前鋒]]。

== 球員生涯 ==
碧福特出身於[[切尔西足球俱乐部|車路士]]青訓<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.glorygloryleedsunited.com/2007/11/beckford-wipes-off-chelseas-grin.html |title=Beckford wipes off Chelsea's grin |access-date=2008-05-24 |archive-date=2008-05-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080514060749/http://www.glorygloryleedsunited.com/2007/11/beckford-wipes-off-chelseas-grin.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，及後轉投[[石威德足球會|石威德]]，碧福特在石威德有非常驚人的表現，上陣40次，一共為球隊轟入35球。

2006年3月15日，列斯聯在一眾競爭球會中，以4.5萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]簽下了碧福特<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/l/leeds_united/4810094.stm |title=Leeds win race to sign Beckford |accessdate=2008-05-24 |archive-date=2012-08-09 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/69nYdHuzJ?url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/leeds_united/4810094.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，首場上陣是在2006年3月迎戰[[水晶宫足球俱乐部|水晶宮]] ，及後，碧福特被外借至[[卡莱尔联足球俱乐部|卡素爾]]<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/c/carlisle_united/5410490.stm |title=Carlisle snap up Beckford on loan |accessdate=2008-05-24 |archive-date=2006-11-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061128031435/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/c/carlisle_united/5410490.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，於2007年1月外借至[[斯坎索普足球俱乐部|斯肯索普]]<small><ref>[http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/scunthorpe_utd/6279525.stm  Scunthorpe land striker Beckford]</ref></small>，碧福特曾表示希望轉投斯肯索普 ，但被當時的列斯聯領隊[[丹尼斯·韋斯|丹尼斯·韋斯]]拒絕。

在2007/08年球季，碧福特攻入該季的第一球，助球隊4-1大勝[[修安聯足球會|修安聯]] 。及後，在列斯聯對[[諾定咸森林足球會|諾定咸森林]]的賽事中，碧福特臨完場前的入球助球隊以2-1獲勝。

2007年10月11日，碧福特與列斯聯簽下3年合約<small><ref>[http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/l/leeds_united/7040046.stm   Beckford pens new Leeds contract]</ref></small>，其後在1月轉會市場開啟後，當時[[英格蘭足球超級聯賽|英超]]球會[[德比郡足球俱乐部|打比郡]]表示希望碧福特加盟，列斯聯在2008年1月8日對外表明碧福特是不會出售的<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.leedsunited.com/page/NewsroomDetail/0,,10273~1209490,00.html |title=JERMAINE BECKFORD |access-date=2008-05-24 |archive-date=2008-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080112063703/http://www.leedsunited.com/page/NewsroomDetail/0,,10273~1209490,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

2008年3月2日，碧福特榮獲[[英格蘭足球甲級聯賽|英甲]]年度最佳球員獎<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.football-league.premiumtv.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10794~1255004,00.html |title=http://www.football-league.premiumtv.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10794~1255004,00.html |access-date=2008-05-24 |archive-date=2008-07-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080724083657/http://www.football-league.premiumtv.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0%2C%2C10794~1255004%2C00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，另外，碧福特在外借至[[斯肯索普足球俱樂部|斯肯索普]]期間對[[羅瑟勒姆足球俱樂部|洛達咸]]的入球亦成為[[英格蘭足球聯賽|英格蘭足球聯賽]]年度金球<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.football-league.premiumtv.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10794~1255098,00.html |title=Jermaine Beckford Wins Goal Of The Year Award At 2008 Football League Awards |access-date=2008-05-24 |archive-date=2008-07-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080724083313/http://www.football-league.premiumtv.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0%2C%2C10794~1255098%2C00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

2009年5月21日碧福特以34個總入球獲得「英甲彪馬金靴獎」（Purma Golden Boot）<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |title=League honour golden six |url=http://www.football-league.co.uk/page/LatestNewsDetail/0,,10794~1661381,00.html |publisher=[[英格蘭足球聯賽|''football-league.co.uk'']] |date=2009-05-21 |accessdate=2009-05-22 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090522184809/http://www.football-league.co.uk/page/LatestNewsDetail/0%2C%2C10794~1661381%2C00.html |archivedate=2009-05-22 }}</ref></small>。

2009年12月份的6場聯賽碧福特射入4球，使他獲選該月「英甲每月最佳球員」<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.football-league.co.uk/league1/news/beckford-named-player-of-the-month-20100109_2248206_1927600 |title=BECKFORD NAMED PLAYER OF THE MONTH |publisher=[[英格蘭足球聯賽|''football-league.co.uk'']] |date=2010-01-09 |accessdate=2010-01-12 }}{{dead link|date=2018年4月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref></small>。2010年1月3日在[[英格蘭足總盃|英格蘭足總盃]]面對超級聯賽球隊[[曼聯|曼聯]]射進全場唯一入球，協助球隊自1982年起首次在[[奧脫福球場|奧脫福球場]]擊敗曼聯。但在賽前他已向球隊提出轉會要求，傳聞將會加盟[[英冠|英冠]]球會[[纽卡斯尔联足球俱乐部|紐卡素]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/leeds_united/8444552.stm |title=Leeds striker Jermaine Beckford puts in transfer request |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-01-06 |accessdate=2010-01-07 |archive-date=2010-01-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100107030033/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/leeds_united/8444552.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。於季後約滿的碧福特在1月17日撤回轉會要求，留隊直到球季結束，全力為球隊完成升班任務<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/leeds_united/8464263.stm |title=Jermaine Beckford to finish season at Leeds United |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-01-17 |accessdate=2010-01-18 |archive-date=2010-01-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100120081604/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/leeds_united/8464263.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。3月14日，他在「英格蘭聯賽頒獎禮」獲選為「英格蘭甲級聯賽年度最佳球員」<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.football-league.co.uk/flawards/news/20100314/league-1-player-of-the-year_2246530_1992269 |title=LEAGUE 1 PLAYER OF THE YEAR |publisher=[[英格蘭足球聯賽|''football-league.co.uk'']] |date=2010-03-14 |accessdate=2010-03-16 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100322205454/http://www.football-league.co.uk/flawards/news/20100314/league-1-player-of-the-year_2246530_1992269 |archivedate=2010-03-22 }}</ref></small>。

2010年5月28日列斯聯提早解除與碧福特將於6月尾才屆滿的合約<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/leeds_united/8711429.stm |title=Leeds United cancel Jermaine Beckford's contract early |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-05-28 |accessdate=2011-09-03 |archive-date=2010-06-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100602044732/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/leeds_united/8711429.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，5月31日，碧福特以自由身加盟[[英超|英超]]球會[[埃弗顿足球俱乐部|愛華頓]]，簽約4年<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/e/everton/8714418.stm |title=Everton sign former Leeds striker Jermaine Beckford |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-05-31 |accessdate=2011-09-03 |archive-date=2012-08-09 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/69nYfNkjQ?url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/e/everton/8714418.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，效力期間在聯賽上陣34場及射入8球，惟一直未能成功融入球隊。

2011年8月31日於增加出價至400萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]後，[[英冠|英冠]]球會[[莱斯特城足球俱乐部|莱斯特城]]成功羅致碧福特<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/14734145.stm |title=Jermaine Beckford leaves Everton for Leicester City |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-08-31 |accessdate=2011-09-03 |archive-date=2011-09-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110901225346/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/14734145.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2012年9月28日，獲升上[[英冠|英冠]]作賽的[[哈德斯菲尔德足球俱乐部|哈特斯菲爾德]]成功向另一[[英冠|英冠]]球會[[莱斯特城足球俱乐部|莱斯特城]]借用碧福特至2013年1月<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/19765746 |title=Jermaine Beckford moves on loan to Huddersfield from Leicester |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2012-09-28 |accessdate=2013-10-01 |archive-date=2013-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131017185853/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/19765746 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2012年12月24日，碧福特獲[[莱斯特城足球俱乐部|莱斯特城]]同意繼續由[[哈德斯菲尔德足球俱乐部|哈特斯菲爾德]]借用至球季結朿<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/20836921 |title=Huddersfield Town extend Jermaine Beckford's loan |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2012-12-24 |accessdate=2013-10-01 |archive-date=2012-12-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121231213835/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/20836921 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2013年7月17日，[[英冠|英冠]]球會[[博尔顿足球俱乐部|博尔顿]]成功向[[莱斯特城足球俱乐部|莱斯特城]]購入碧福特，轉會費金額沒有透露，合約為期兩年<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/23159639 |title=Jermaine Beckford: Bolton sign Leicester striker |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2013-07-17 |accessdate=2013-10-01 |archive-date=2013-12-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131208131348/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/23159639 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

